# Footlight — optional environment configuration. Copy to `.env` (gitignored)
# or just `export` these in your shell.
#
# BYOK Gemini API key for the optional AI features (subject tracking + the
# assistant). When set, it is used by the CLI and by `make gui`, and it takes
# precedence over any key stored in the desktop app's OS keychain (so a native
# app launched from a shell with this set won't prompt for keychain access).
# AI is entirely optional — Footlight's core cut/crop/scale/encode never needs a key.
# Get a key at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=
